'''Spouse:''' * Shima-ko, daughter of {{ill|Matsudaira Mitsunori|ja|松平光則|12=draft|12=draft}}
'''Adopted Son:''' * {{ill|Toda Tadayuki (adopted son)|ja|戸田忠友|12=draft|12=draft}}, eldest son of {{ill|Toda Tadashi|ja|戸田忠偲|12=draft|12=draft}}
