'''Spouse:''' * Shima-ko, daughter of [[:en:Matsudaira Mitsuhisa|Matsudaira Mitsunori]]
'''Adopted Son:''' * {{ill|Toda Tadayuki (adopted son)|ja|戸田忠友|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Toda Tadayuki (adopted son)|qq=}}, eldest son of {{ill|Toda Tadashi|ja|戸田忠偲|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Toda Tadashi|qq=}}
